      "status": "shipped",
      "description": "Implemented a NodeAnnotationProxy system on the canvas. Because canvas cards are QGraphicsItems rather than QWidgets, the annotator was unable to 'see' them. I added invisible QWidgets that shadow each card in the viewport, allowing the annotator to latch onto them while passing all interaction through to the canvas.",
      "change_overview": [
        "apps/gui/canvas/page.py: Added NodeAnnotationProxy class",
        "apps/gui/canvas/page.py: Updated _CanvasViewWithDrop to manage proxies",
        "apps/gui/canvas/page.py: Wired signals for movement, zoom, pan, and undo/redo"
      ],
